tract now, and give the summer conversation another week or two to settle?\n\n\n\"I want to think about the summer piece more carefully — can you send me what you're thinking in writing and give me until [date] to confirm?\"\n\n\"I take these commitments seriously, and I don't want to say yes to something I can't fully deliver on. Give me a week to think it through properly.\"",
